=== Marginalized_Groups ===
Social media bans affect users differently. # diagram: marginalized_isolation.jpg

For some young people, online communities provide connections unavailable locally:
• Youth in areas with few nearby peers
• Those whose interests or backgrounds aren't represented locally
• Young people with mobility limitations

