=== Research_Reality ===
Absolutely true—social media isn't perfect or safe.

But Australian research on their school phone ban shows bans might reduce some harms, but also restrict positive experiences—particularly social support for marginalized groups.

The question isn't "Is social media harmful?" It's "Is a complete ban better than teaching safer use?"

